snippet.title: Sonic Advance Revamped SAGE 2018 Trailer Clip (READ DESCRIPTION)
snippet.description:
The email containing the clip of Sonic Advance Revamped meant for the SAGE 2018 Trailer was lost to the ether of Gmail. However, I have uploaded it for your Ten-Second Viewing Pleasure ahead of SAGE! Here it is in all its Ten Second Glory! See you all at SAGE!!

HUGE thanks to Garrulous64 for putting this together! Link to his channel below!

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCGkdmqlRSI4jeH-KHP0Spg
